PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Product Discovery App
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app helps you discover new and innovative products across various categories. We curate the latest product launches, unique finds, and trending items to keep you updated.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How does the product discovery process work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our team of experts scours the market for exciting new products. We evaluate them based on factors like innovation, quality, and user reviews before featuring them on our app.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What categories of products can I find?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: We cover a wide range of categories including technology, home and kitchen, fashion, beauty, fitness, and more. Our app caters to diverse interests and lifestyles.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is the app free to use?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, our app is completely free to download and use. We don't charge any membership fees or subscriptions. Our goal is to provide a seamless product discovery experience.

FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, the app is completely free to download and use. We may introduce premium features in the future, but the core product discovery experience will always be free.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I filter products by category?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! You can easily filter products by categories like electronics, home & garden, fashion, beauty, and more. This way, you only see new products relevant to your interests.

FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Our product databases are updated multiple times per day to ensure you always have access to the latest releases as soon as they hit the market.
